{"tid":2330603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歌舞群組｜追訪確診國產舞郎 1屋16床7人中招","createTime":"2020-12-18T07:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T10:19:03.000Z","uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e49d1729c9a737e4eab974de73200a75c40c9646","tid":2330603,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:00:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GMCRtJOZRkc?t=25\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGMCRtJOZRkc%3Ft%3D25&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=29281b9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GMCRtJOZRkc?t=25</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201218/HSWFJVKPSRDMLNRD3XDS5PIFGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201218%2FHSWFJVKPSRDMLNRD3XDS5PIFGY%2F&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=ea285159\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201218%2FHSWFJVKPSRDMLNRD3XDS5PIFGY%2F&h=306f143a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201218/HSWFJVKPSRDMLNRD3XDS5PIFGY/</a><br />\n引爆本港第四波疫情的歌舞群組至今發酵近一個月，截至昨日 (17日)下午5時，歌舞群組已有726人中招， 釀成6人死，病毒更擴散醫院、老人院、令多個屋苑頓成疫區，為本港疫情爆發近一年以來，傳播力最驚人的感染群組。《蘋果》追查發現，今次大爆發，傳播鏈之一來自一群疫情下來港「搵食」的內地跳舞老師，他們流連舞場陪舞，再將病毒帶回宿舍，令全屋人中招！記者直擊旺角一個爆疫老師宿舍，發現一屋16個床位，全屋至少7人中招！<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：歌舞群組｜跳舞也分級 富婆最愛請世界級老師攞威<br />\n「就是那個叫孔龍的內地跳舞老師，跟他同房兩人都中招了，挺冤的， (其他人)一聽到這個消息馬上就跑了！」住旺角利民大廈疫屋的內地人Jason透露，屋內原本住有8至9人，爆疫後只剩他一人。<br />\n<br />\n據衞生署資料，利民大廈全幢最少9人染疫，當中7人是歌舞群組，(編號：5533、5588、5660、5662、5665、5666、6544)，當中至少5人非香港居民，據知他們全部住在利民大廈同一單位，記者日前直擊該爆疫單位，發現面積500呎、3房1廳，但全屋擺有8張碌架鐵床，提供16個床位，每張床之間走廊狹窄，僅以布簾隔開，床邊則掛有不少衣物及內衣褲，床上擺滿雜物等，屋內廚廁共用，衞生惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G2F_etH7sMY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG2F_etH7sMY&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=e20e8416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G2F_etH7sMY</a>"},{"pid":"a0d23d8850181e1cb209c137373860b592a88e68","tid":2330603,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eaceb39401dbca31cfead7d1da65291704e4387","tid":2330603,"uid":50423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"孔龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb24871087212c3ba4358c8feaee76715688512","tid":2330603,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a0d23d8850181e1cb209c137373860b592a88e68","tid":2330603,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69af09169694bd89cfbf0f27765cbe3198e0bf1","tid":2330603,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0eaceb39401dbca31cfead7d1da65291704e4387","tid":2330603,"uid":50423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"孔龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}